  "texts": [
    "Empirically, this property has also been observed, e.g., [21, To study the optimality of π ⋆ p (λ ⋆ p) w/ π ⋆, we first bound the gap between λ ⋆ p and λ ⋆ in Lemma 4.",
    "Lemma 4 (Dual gap).",
    "Let Assumptions 3 and 5 hold.",
    "Then, the difference between λ ⋆ p and λ ⋆ satisfiesλ ⋆ p -λ ⋆ ≤ 2 µ ⋆ D M + β + M λ ⋆ p 1 ν.See the proof of Lemma 4 in Appendix B.5.",
    "Lemma 4 shows that the gap between λ p and λ ⋆ is of order √ ν."
